{"word":"H2664 - חָפַשׂ - châphas - khaw-fas' - Change","slug":"H2664","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָפַשׂ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>châphas"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khaw-fas'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Change"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D7;&#x05E4;&#x05E9;&#x05C2; - cha&#x0302;phas&#x0301;</b> - <i>khaw-fas'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>seek</i>; causatively to <i>conceal</i> oneself (that is, let be sought), or <i>mask: - </i>change, (make) diligent (search), disguise self, hide, search (for, out)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2665\">H2665</a>"}]}